description: Gets a list of labeling jobs.

nested_items.name: LabelingJobSummaryList
nested_items.description: An array of LabelingJobSummary objects, each describing a labeling job.

nested_items.name: LabelingJobName
nested_items.description: The name of the labeling job.

nested_items.name: LabelingJobArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) assigned to the labeling job when it was created.

nested_items.name: CreationTime
nested_items.description: The date and time that the job was created (timestamp).

nested_items.name: LastModifiedTime
nested_items.description: The date and time that the job was last modified (timestamp).

nested_items.name: LabelingJobStatus
nested_items.description: The current status of the labeling job.

nested_items.name: LabelCounters
nested_items.description: Counts showing the progress of the labeling job.

nested_items.name: TotalLabeled
nested_items.description: The total number of objects labeled.

nested_items.name: HumanLabeled
nested_items.description: The total number of objects labeled by a human worker.

nested_items.name: MachineLabeled
nested_items.description: The total number of objects labeled by automated data labeling.

nested_items.name: FailedNonRetryableError
nested_items.description: The total number of objects that could not be labeled due to an error.

nested_items.name: Unlabeled
nested_items.description: The total number of objects not yet labeled.

nested_items.name: WorkteamArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the work team assigned to the job.

nested_items.name: PreHumanTaskLambdaArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of a Lambda function. The function is run before each data object is sent to a worker.

nested_items.name: AnnotationConsolidationLambdaArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Lambda function used to consolidate the annotations from individual workers into a label for a data object. For more information, see Annotation Consolidation.

nested_items.name: FailureReason
nested_items.description: If the LabelingJobStatus field is Failed, this field contains a description of the error.

nested_items.name: LabelingJobOutput
nested_items.description: The location of the output produced by the labeling job.

nested_items.name: OutputDatasetS3Uri
nested_items.description: The Amazon S3 bucket location of the manifest file for labeled data.

nested_items.name: FinalActiveLearningModelArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for the most recent SageMaker model trained as part of automated data labeling.

nested_items.name: InputConfig
nested_items.description: Input configuration for the labeling job.

nested_items.name: DataSource
nested_items.description: The location of the input data.

nested_items.name: S3DataSource
nested_items.description: The Amazon S3 location of the input data objects.

nested_items.name: ManifestS3Uri
nested_items.description: The Amazon S3 location of the manifest file that describes the input data objects.
source-ref: The source of the object is the Amazon S3 object specified in the value. Use this value when the object is a binary object, such as an image.
source: The source of the object is the value. Use this value when the object is a text value.

nested_items.name: SnsDataSource
nested_items.description: An Amazon SNS data source used for streaming labeling jobs. To learn more, see Send Data to a Streaming Labeling Job.

nested_items.name: SnsTopicArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon SNS input topic Amazon Resource Name (ARN). Specify the ARN of the input topic you will use to send new data objects to a streaming labeling job.

nested_items.name: DataAttributes
nested_items.description: Attributes of the data specified by the customer.

nested_items.name: ContentClassifiers
nested_items.description: Declares that your content is free of personally identifiable information or adult content. SageMaker may restrict the Amazon Mechanical Turk workers that can view your task based on this information.
(string) ---

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If the response is truncated, SageMaker returns this token. To retrieve the next set of labeling jobs, use it in the subsequent request.
